&lt;p>K8sCommerce is a headless ecommerce platform architected from the ground-up to be cloud native
and run on Kubernetes. It is comprised of 14 microservices, 2 public/web facing via a JSON REST API,
and 12 private/non-web facing RPC services.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="json-rest-api-facing-services">JSON REST API Facing Services:&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>There are 2 &lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/microservices/public-facing-json">Public-Facing JSON Services&lt;/a>.
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>A &lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/microservices/public-facing-json/client">client&lt;/a> service that exposes all necessary &lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/client">client endpoints&lt;/a> to facilitate a headless storefront
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/client/cart">Cart&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/client/customer">Customer&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/client/catalog">Catalog&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/client/payment">Payments&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>An &lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/microservices/public-facing-json/admin">admin&lt;/a> service that exposes all &lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin">administration endpoints&lt;/a> required to manage the K8sCommerce platform:
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/cart">Cart&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/catalog">Catalog&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/customer">Customer&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/email">Email&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/inventory">Inventory&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/othersbought">Others Bought&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/payment">Payment&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/shipping">Shipping&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/similarproducts">Similar Products&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/store">Store&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/user">User&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://k8scommerce.github.io/docs/rest-endpoints/admin/warehouse">Warehouse&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
